---
title: "Skills — The Agent ↔ Binary Protocol"
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as 👤 Developer
    participant Master as 🤖 Master
    participant Primer as 🔍 Primer
    participant Skill as 📜 Skill File
    participant CX as ⚙️ cx binary
    participant Docs as 📁 docs/
    participant Mem as 🧠 docs/memories/
    participant Sup as 👷 Supervisor
    participant MCP as 🔌 Linear MCP

    Note over Dev,Mem: Session Start

    Dev->>Master: "Let's work on the gas alerting feature"

    Master->>Primer: Spawns Primer (passes message)
    Primer->>Skill: Reads cx-prime.md skill
    Skill-->>Primer: "Classify mode, call cx context --mode, distill"
    Primer->>CX: cx context --mode build
    CX->>Docs: Reads specs, memories, changes
    Docs-->>CX: Context map
    CX-->>Primer: Structured map of available context
    Primer->>CX: cx context --load spec gas-monitoring
    CX-->>Primer: Full spec content
    Primer-->>Master: Returns ~600 tokens of distilled context

    Master->>Master: Classifies task → team dispatch

    Note over Dev,Mem: Brainstorm Phase (Master handles directly)

    Master->>Skill: Reads cx-brainstorm.md skill
    Master->>CX: cx brainstorm
    CX->>Docs: Creates masterfile.md template
    CX-->>Master: Template path + instructions
    Master->>Docs: Fills masterfile.md with structured intent

    Dev->>Master: "Also consider the firmware side"
    Master->>Docs: Edits masterfile.md with new firmware considerations

    Dev->>Master: "Looks good, let's go"

    Note over Dev,Mem: Decompose Phase

    Master->>CX: cx decompose
    CX->>Docs: Creates docs/changes/fix-gas-alerts/ structure
    CX->>Docs: Archives masterfile → docs/archive/
    CX-->>Master: "Change created. Fill templates."
    Master->>Docs: Fills proposal.md, design.md, tasks.md
    Master->>MCP: Create Linear issues via MCP
    MCP-->>Master: Issues created

    Note over Dev,Mem: Implementation Phase (Team Dispatch)

    Master->>Sup: Spawns Supervisor with task + context
    Sup->>Sup: Spawns Scout → explores codebase
    Sup->>Sup: Spawns Contractor → spawns Workers
    Note over Sup: Workers write code, Contractor reviews
    Sup->>CX: cx memory save --title "Gas threshold uses INT not FLOAT"
    CX->>Mem: Writes observation .md file
    Sup->>MCP: Updates Linear issue status
    Sup-->>Master: Reports completion

    Note over Dev,Mem: Archive Phase

    Master->>CX: cx change archive fix-gas-alerts
    CX->>Docs: Validates, merges delta → specs, moves to archive
    CX->>Mem: Writes completion summary
    CX-->>Master: "Archived. Specs updated."
